column3: Heavensturn is a chance anew, yes? I am thinking it is like the game\xe2\x94\x80rock, silk, claw.

The hand is coming up, the hand is making shapes, the hand is winning, losing, or tying. Every Heavensturn, the hand is coming up. Chance, \x02\x08\x13\xe9\x05\xff\x07m'lady\xff\x07m'lord\x03, chance.
You are losing the crimson uma kabuto? Sometimes, I am thinking you are not very smart.
Does \x02\x08\x13\xe9\x05\xff\x07m'lady\xff\x07m'lord\x03 sniffle? Another one in your hands, I am thinking, will dry those tears.
